title: Au Naturel
description:
Health food shop where everything is organic. Fresh vegetable and fruits
from local producers, spices, herbs, dried bulk food, grains, flour, yeast, raw chocolate, energy bars, nut butters, soymilk, juices, tofu, aged miso, frozen non-dairy ice cream and treats, wide variety of frozen veggie sausages, burgers, tempeh, and frozen vegan diner.
